•   inv.(n+1) ≡ ?

⊩   inv.(n+1)

≡   Definition of inv

    (n :: r = mss.n ∧ 0 ≤ n ∧ n ≤ N).(n+1)

≡   λ comp

    r = mss.(n+1) ∧ 0 ≤ n+1 ∧ n+1 ≤ N

≡   Property of mss (Theory[3])

    r = mss(n) ↑ f.(n+1) ∧ 0 ≤ n+1 ∧ n+1 ≤ N

≡   Property of f (Theory[5])

    r = mss(n) ↑ ((f.n + a.n) ↑ 0) ∧ 0 ≤ n+1 ∧ n+1 ≤ N

■